data.title: FT8 & Solar – Turbine Technical Information – Training and Troubleshooting documentation and videos.
data.text:
“GET STARTED”

Download the site content index. Press the download button and you will have the index withing three seconds. No registering, no email, no credit card.

Take a look at the list of articles to see if this is the type of material you are looking for. There is a description of some of the articles (work in progress). If the contents is of interest and you would like to continue you must complete the “Site Registration”Â Â

“SITE REGISTRATION”

Unfortunately this has to be done manulaly as I am getting a lot of SPAM registrations that I have to delete manually. So select “contact me” from the Main Page or send me a WhatsApp and I will set up.

“SITE LOGIN”

Use the information you provided to register to login. Select “Remember Me” to not have to enter the password again.

“FINDING INFORMATION”

Open the Excel Index you downloaded. Note that the list has a column for Free or Premium content. This lets you know whether you have to pay or not for an item.

Because of the large number of articles and videos, you need a simple way of finding the informaiton. Use the excel sheet as follows:

1) Turn “FILTERING ON” for this spreadsheet.

2) Select from the “OEM” filter.

3) Select from from the “CATEGORIES” filter.

4) Note the “ARTICLE REF” of the articles / videos ofÂ interest (example ART022)

5) Go to my website main page www.dmba5411.com

6) Then use the “Keyword Search” and type in the “Article Ref” and press “Search”.

“SUBSCRIPTION”

To purchase the Subscription go to my “Store” at the top of my “Home Page” and you can purchase “one month access” or” permanent access” to the database of documents and videso. Permanent is for a minimum of one year or for as long as the site is active.

“TRAINING”

To purchase training courses go to my “Store” at the top of my “Home Page”. There you will see the courses for sale.
